        <h1>SafePath Advocacy</h1>
        <p>At SafePath, we are committed to advocating for a safe and supportive environment for all students. Our mission is to raise awareness about bullying and promote resources that help students seek assistance and report incidents effectively.</p>
        
        <h2>Our Advocacy Goals</h2>
        <ul>
            
            <li>Raise awareness about bullying and its impacts on mental health.</li>
            <li>Provide resources and support for victims of bullying.</li>
            <li>Encourage open communication between students and school authorities.</li>
            <li>Foster a culture of kindness and respect within the educational community.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Join Us in Making a Difference</h2>
        <p>We believe that every student has the right to a safe learning environment. Join us in our efforts to advocate for change and support those in need. Together, we can create a positive impact in our community.</p>

        <h2>How You Can Help</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Participate in awareness campaigns and events.</li>
            <li>Share your story to inspire others.</li>
            <li>Volunteer with local organizations focused on bullying prevention.</li>
            <li>Spread the word about SafePath and our mission.</li>
        </ul>
